zm_fortress_b7 - Changelog

Created by [#OMEGA] - K2

Preface: This is my first offical multiplayer map; I deceided to create a zombie mod because zombie mod owns. Orginally it was crated for a clan out of a HLÂ² Map (which was created just for SP ^^), but this clan kicked me so I won't work for the clan anymore. This map is independent now ^^
Map Information: This is somekind of a fortress build by humans and overtaken by the combines during the war. Now it is abonded and the combine and thair human slaves disappeared without a trace. Blood and somekind of "Headcrabs" were found here; according to roumors zombies were seen in the fortress... Now it's about you to find out what really happened here... Good Luck soldier!

  • changed storage room 3 (improved spots)
  • balanced the spot over the stairs (it will break with 2 or more cts)
  • changed the office room connected to the vent (hopefully a bit more useful now)
  • changed the room connected to the sewers (props added)
  • Unnecessary faces removed:
    • bedrooms
    • entrace room (next to t spawn)
    • (100+) in the computer room (above t spawn)
    • on the railings...
    • sewers room
    • bathrooms
    • canals entrances(removed 16 brushes per entrance too)
  • removed a litte bug in the sewers room
  • added/improved spots in the computer room (above t spawn)
  • applied some prop fade dists to some stuff in the computer room (above t spawn)
  • increased the length of the way to the first bedroom
  • fixed some bush sizes
  • map overview added
  • some fade distances changed and min fade dists for some props added
  • the secrets in the bathroom were fixed (finally... omg)
  • Lightning changes:
    • HDR Lightning
    • Overall lightning is darker now
    • Added lightblockers to the sewers entrances (surfrace)
    • Added lightblocker to the door in the sewer room
    • Added lightblocker to computer room (above t spawn)

    • Amout of lights reduced
    • light colors in every area changed
    • fixed guardhouse light
  • some unnecessary cubemaps removed
  • some cubemap sizes reduced in dark areas and in certain rooms
  • new spot added (trash dumpster)
  • fixed 2 texture bugs in the bathroom
  • added new skybox
  • removed some ambient sounds
  • added a lot of soundscapes
  • fixed a texture bug in way between the bombsite and the storage room (next to the sewer entrance)
  • fixed a texture bug in the big vent
  • the radios emit sounds now ;)
  • some existing areaportals have been improved
  • some more areaportals have been added
  • occluder sizes fixed
  • ads added
Planned for new Versions:
  • rework of some more lights
  • .nav file with place names (FINAL RELEASE)
  • adding some more props
  • ragdolls/blood
  • [decals (maybe more)]
  • [Sounds (maybe more)]
  • using higher/better lightmaps
Always planned:
  • bugfixes (If I find some or someone report bugs)
  • balancing
Installation: Just do the following steps to install the map:
  • copy the folders except fastdl into your ..\cstrike\ folder
  • add the map to your mapcycle.txt/maplist.txt/votemaplist.txt
  • if you are using sv_downloadurl upload the contents of fastdl to your webserver

This is a rock floating in the sky with a house built on it, some trees and other stuff. It contains mostly climbing spots but also some for barricading. Thanks to hipshot for the nice skybox texture! [Features:] - 64 spawn points - cubemaps - no falling damage (you get teleported back up) - climbing and barricading/camping spots - good framerate [Update History:] --- v2 (01.04.2010) --- v2 is still available for download here (for smaller servers). - Fixed invalid spawn points - Fixed falling damage bug (some players DID receive damage) - Added some more hiding spots - Improved design slightly in some places - Made one hiding spot easier accessible (the 3 small floating rocks) --- v3 (03.04.2010) --- - Enlarged the map - Connected various camping spots / made them easier accessible --- v4 (04.04.2010) --- - Made the tree easier accessible - Fixed a spot where you could get stuck - Players don't get stuck anymore when being teleported --- v5 (19.04.2010) --- - Added another barricading room inside the main rock - Made the camping spot inside the smaller rock easier accessible (there are more small crates instead of big ones now) - Some more minor changes [Known bug:] On a server where killed zombies respawn as humans the respawned humans get falling damage.. and thus die when they fall down. (Although I added an extra trigger in front of the teleports. There seems to be no solution for this problem) >> Click here to look for servers where this map is running! <<

Updated
=======
This map is an update of zm\_FireWaLL\_forestoutpost (http://gamebanana.com/csszm/maps/148209)

Introduction
============
Zombies are launching an assault on an outpost in the forest. Defend yourselves by blocking them with all sorts of obstacles, or find some high ground to fend yourselves from the zombies!

Features
========
- 64 + 64 spawnpoints
- Cubemaps
- Optimized
- Secrets

Changelog
=========
- The "hole" underneath the two-desk-room has been covered with a breakable wooden floor. Now you need to break it first. The cabinets underneath the desks are now physic props.
- The underground room design has been improved significantly.
- Shortcuts (ladders) up the tower have been added for balance reasons.
- Zombies should find it harder, if not impossible, to jump from the tower onto the tree-platform now.
- Map is now slightly brighter.
- Various textures have been replaced and improved
- New secrets have been added.

I have ensured that every spot is useful, so every space in this small map area can be fully utilised.

-64/64 spawnpoints
-Cubemaps (compiled)
-LDR
-Compiled in Normal BSP, VIS and RAD
-Good FPS
